==== Dr Jean Paul NGARUKIYIMANA ====
yavukiye mu [[Rwanda]] mu mwaka w’I 1989 akaba arinaho yize

amashuri abanza n’ayisumbuye ndetse n’icyiro cya mbere cya kaminuza (Bachelor) . Nyuma yo

kurangiza Kaminuza 2012, mu ishami ry’ubugenge muri [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|Kaminuza y’ u Rwanda]] yahise ajya

gukomereza amasomo ye mu gihugu cy’[[ubushinwa]] . Kuva muwa 2012 yize ururimi rw’igishinwa

muri kaminuza ya [[Chonqing Normal University]] <ref>http://ncclcs.ncc-cma.net/Website/index.php?ChannelID=142&NewsID=3241</ref>  ahava ajya kwiga icyiciro cya kabiri cya

kaminuza mu mujyi wa Nanjing muri kaminuza ya [https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nanjing_University_of_Information_Science_and_Technology Nanjing University of Information Science and]

[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nanjing_University_of_Information_Science_and_Technology Technology]  mu ishami ry’ubumenyi muby’ikirere (Master of science in meteorology).<ref>https://news.nuist.edu.cn/2015/0330/c1150a82262/page.htm</ref>

=== Ibikorwa by'indashyikirwa ===
Mugihe yigaga ikicyiro cyakabiri cya kaminuza yabaye umwe mubanyeshuri bindashyikrwa <ref>https://www.wcrp-climate.org/s2s-s2d-2018-posters/s2s-s2d-2018-list-posters</ref> ahabwa
[[File:Dr Jean Paul in interview with China Meteorological Agency journalist (6th August 2018).jpg|thumb|Impuguke mumuhindagurikire y, ikirere]]
n’inshingano zo kuyobora bagenzi be biga ibijyanye n’ubumenyi mu by’ikirere<ref>https://news.nuist.edu.cn/2015/0330/c1150a82262/page.htm</ref>. Amaze

kurangiza Icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza yakomereje muri Kaminuza ya [[University ofScience and Technology of China|University of]]

[[University ofScience and Technology of China|Science and Technology  China]] (USTC) imwe muri kaminuza za mbere zikomeye mu gihugu

cy’ubushinwa,<ref>https://en.ustc.edu.cn/</ref> ahakura impamyabumenyi y’ikirenga (PhD) mu bumenyi bw’isi n’ikirere. Dr Jean

Paul yabaye umuyobozi wa USTC -African students Association (ASU) na USTC- Foreign Students

Association ubwo yigaga muri USTC Kuva muri Mata 2021.

